1/31 * 2^t  => A * B^(t/10 - 1)

= 1/31 * 2^(10 * t/10)

= 1/31 * (2^10)^(t/10)        //(a^b)^c = a^(bc)

= 1/31 * 1024^(t/10)

= 1/31 * 1024^(t/10 - 1 + 1)

= 1/31 * 1024^(t/10 - 1) * 1024    //a^b * a^c = a^(b + c)

= 1024/31 * 1024^(t/10 - 1)

= 2^10/2^5 * 1024^(t/10 - 1)

= 32 * 1024^(t/10 - 1)
